		"description": {
			"value": "<p><em>Wondrous Item - Very Rare (Requires Attunement)</em></p><p><em>This black or dark-blue robe is embroidered with small white or silver stars.</em></p><p><em>A magic item like this grants a bonus to checks where relevant and counts as magical for overcoming effects.</em></p><p><strong>Buff</strong></p><ul><li><p>You gain a +1 bonus to saving throws while you wear it.</p></li></ul><p><strong>Activation</strong> - 6 Charges (Regains [[/r 1d6]] at Dusk)</p><ul><li><p><strong>Action</strong> (1 Charge) - Remove a large star to cast <em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.wZJ04LVK8K0jSm1B]{Magic Missile}</em> at level 5.</p></li></ul><p><strong>Action</strong> - Enter/Exit Astral Plane</p><ul><li><p>Enter the Astral Plane with all worn/carried gear. Remain until you take an Action to return, reappearing in your last space (or nearest unoccupied space if occupied).</p></li></ul><section id=\"foundry-secret-1\" class=\"secret\"><p><strong>Foundry Note</strong></p><p>The <strong>Enter/Exit Astral Plane</strong> activity includes a 5-foot template to mark your exit location.</p></section>",
